HEADWORD: Wait-a-while
<hw>Wait"-a-while`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sd>(a)</sd> <def>One of the
Australian wattle trees (<spn>Acacia colletioides</spn>), so called from
the impenetrability of the thicket which it makes.</def> <sd>(b)</sd>
<def>same as <er>Wait-a-bit</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

